text: Oliwia Bałuk (born ) is a Polish female volleyball player. She is part of the Poland women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2017 Girls' U18 Volleyball European Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League.
